                <note rend="inline" type="source">815.00/2701: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morales</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-10-08T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1923—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>41. With reference to Legation’s No. 80, October 5, 2 p.m., you will of course
                    not comply with request of the private secretary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
